name: DuelingPistols
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dueling pistols wine
des:
This skill takes you into the world of Dueling Pistols Wines. 
Find out about the wines, vines, regions and blends, experience a guided tasting with characters from the label talking to you. 

You can say 'Learn about Dueling Pistols' , 'Guided Tasting', or 'Find the Wines'.
'Learn about Dueling Pistols' will give you information about the wines.
'Guided Tasting' will ask you what wine you have and give you an interactive tasting experience with audio clips from one of the men on the label.
'Find the Wines' will let you know where to buy the wines.
